# Default Dev Mode Rule

- Default workflow is hybrid: backend via Docker script and frontend local script.
- Unless the user asks otherwise, prefer:
  - `bash scripts/dev_api_docker.sh`
  - `bash scripts/dev_frontend.sh`
- Use full Docker mode (`bash scripts/dev_all_docker.sh` or docker scripts directly) only when explicitly requested or when local Bun tooling is unavailable.
- Keep docs and script references aligned whenever startup commands change.
